==Description==
The '''Everstone''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Everstone has a value of 3 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Everstone appears in the Underground as a 4x2 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:EverstoneMine 0-7-3.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Everstones can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], as [[Rare Hold Items]] from [[File:Geodude.png|30px]] Geodude, [[File:Roggenrola.png|30px]] Roggenrola, [[File:Boldore.png|30px]] Boldore, and [[File:Gigalith.png|30px]] Gigalith, and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

